    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Seems the issue is in `pandas.core.resample._get_range_edges`, line 1591.\r\n\r\nI think `day_nanos % offset.nanos == 0` should be the other way around. This will only ever evaluate to True for Day(n=1). I’m guessing this wasn’t the inention as it would be overly complicated compared to `day_nanos == offset.nanos`."
